</description><category>how-to</category><category>vlc</category><guid>http://avilpage.com/2014/08/fixing-colors-issues-in-vlc-media.html</guid><pubDate>Tue, 12 Aug 2014 08:57:00 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>